### Authentication
# @name Login
POST {{host}}/api/auth/steam-ticket
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "ticket": "integration-ticket",
    "useNativeAuth": false
}

> {% client.global.set("auth_token", response.body.token); %}

### Map Generate
POST {{host}}/api/game/map/generate
X-Token: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "room": "W39N39",
    "shard": "shard1",
    "sources": 2,
    "terrain": "mixed",
    "keeperLairs": true,
    "overwrite": true
}

### Map Open
POST {{host}}/api/game/map/open
X-Token: {{auth_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "room": "W39N39"
}

### Map Open (Shard Override)
POST {{host}}/api/game/map/open
